spec_data.Name: mingw32-SDL2_image
spec_data.Description:
Simple DirectMedia Layer (SDL2) is a cross-platform multimedia library
designed to provide fast access to the graphics frame buffer and audio
device.  This package contains a simple library for loading images of
various formats (BMP, PPM, PCX, GIF, JPEG, PNG) as SDL2 surfaces.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 08:21:52 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: MinGW Windows port of the Image loading library for SDL2
